---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Dewey" hideSearch>
  <div class="about-page">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <section class="about-section">
        <p>
          Dewey is built by <a href="https://arach.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Arach Tchoupani</a> &mdash;
          a software engineer, 4x CTO, and founder based in Montreal.
          15+ years building products, leading teams, and turning ideas into shipped software
          across startups and companies like Meta.
        </p>
        <p>
          Co-founded Breathe Life (acquired 2022). Previously engineering leadership at Meta
          on Creators & Facebook, senior architect on Starbucks Global E-Commerce,
          VP of Engineering at PhotoShelter, founding CTO at Primary.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Background</h2>
        <div class="about-timeline">
          <div class="about-role">
            <span class="about-role-org">Meta</span>
            <span class="about-role-title">Engineering Leadership, FB Creators</span>
            <span class="about-role-date">2022 &ndash; 2023</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-role">
            <span class="about-role-org">Breathe Life</span>
            <span class="about-role-title">Co-Founder & CTO (acquired 2022)</span>
            <span class="about-role-date">2018 &ndash; 2021</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-role">
            <span class="about-role-org">Starbucks</span>
            <span class="about-role-title">Senior Consultant & Architect, Global E-Commerce</span>
            <span class="about-role-date">2019 &ndash; 2020</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-role">
            <span class="about-role-org">PhotoShelter</span>
            <span class="about-role-title">VP of Engineering</span>
            <span class="about-role-date">2016 &ndash; 2017</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-role">
            <span class="about-role-org">Primary</span>
            <span class="about-role-title">Founding CTO</span>
            <span class="about-role-date">2014 &ndash; 2016</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What I'm building</h2>
        <p>
          I build developer tools, AI-native interfaces, and things that bridge the gap between
          how people think and how machines read. Dewey came out of watching coding assistants
          struggle with real-world codebases &mdash; not because the models are bad, but because
          the docs are.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also make <a href="https://usetalkie.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Talkie</a> (voice-first
          capture for developers), and <a href="https://arach.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">a lot of other things</a> &mdash;
          declarative design systems, spatial note-taking agents, programmatic video tooling.
          I believe typing is a bottleneck and that the best tools meet you where you are.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/arach" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://x.com/arach" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
          <a href="https://arach.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">arach.io</a>
          <a href="https://arach.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">arach.dev</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style is:inline>
    .about-page {
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .about-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-family: var(--heading-font, 'Noto Serif Display', serif);
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--color-text);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .about-body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      font-family: var(--heading-font, 'Noto Serif Display', serif);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--color-text);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    }

    .about-section p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-section a {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .about-section a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ── Timeline ── */
    .about-timeline {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .about-role {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .about-role:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .about-role-org {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .about-role-title {
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
    }

    .about-role-date {
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .about-role {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2px;
      }
      .about-role-date {
        order: -1;
      }
    }

    /* ── Links ── */
    .about-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .about-links a {
      font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }

    .about-links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
